---

---

<section id="about" class="stripes py-20 lg:py-28 relative">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-brand-black border-4 border-brand-black card-shadow flex items-end justify-center overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-yellow/10 via-transparent to-brand-black"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto text-brand-yellow/40" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 22a8 8 0 0 1 16 0z"/>
              </svg>
              <div class="mt-3 font-mono text-[10px] text-brand-yellow/60 tracking-widest">[ replace public/mou.jpg ]</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-5 left-6 right-6 bg-brand-black border-2 border-brand-yellow px-5 py-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
          <span class="display italic text-white text-lg sm:text-xl">Barber & Hauler</span>
          <span class="skew-tag bg-brand-yellow text-brand-black">
            <span class="font-mono font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest flex items-center gap-1">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2c-3 0-5 2-5 5l5 7 5-7c0-3-2-5-5-5z"/></svg>
              LOCAL ROOTS
            </span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="skew-tag bg-brand-black text-brand-yellow mb-5">
          <span class="font-mono font-bold text-xs tracking-widest">THE FACE BEHIND THE TRUCK</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="display text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-brand-black">
          <span class="bg-brand-yellow px-3 py-1">Meet Mou.</span>
        </h2>

        <blockquote class="mt-8 border-l-4 border-brand-yellow pl-5">
          <p class="font-mono text-ink text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed italic">
            &ldquo;Whether I'm giving a clean fade at the barbershop or clearing out a chaotic garage, the goal is always the same: leaving things much better than I found them.&rdquo;
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-ink/85 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            With a deep love for his community, Mou isn't just a guy with a truck. He's your local barber who knows the value of hard work, a good conversation, and taking pride in where you live.
          </p>
          <p>
            He started Neighborhood Hauling to provide a service his neighbors could trust. No corporate runarounds, no hidden fees &mdash; just genuine, friendly muscle. We treat your property with the same respect we treat our own, living by one simple motto: <strong>Keepin' the hood clean.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4 bg-brand-black p-5 max-w-md">
          <div class="size-12 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-black" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 4a3 3 0 1 0 0 6 3 3 0 0 0 0-6zm6 0a3 3 0 1 0 0 6 3 3 0 0 0 0-6zM2 22l8-8 4 4-4 4zm20 0l-8-8-4 4 4 4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="display italic text-white text-xl">Need a Cut?</h4>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs text-white/70 mt-1">Ask Mou about his barbershop hours while he's loading up your junk.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
